  <description>
    <p>
      Cardthropic is a modern GNOME solitaire game built with Rust and
      Libadwaita, featuring polished Klondike and Spider gameplay with 1 to 4
      suit modes. Play seeded deals, run winnability analysis, use smart
      moves, and choose flexible click behavior for faster strategy.
    </p>
    <p>
      Automation includes Wand hints and Robot mode with detailed move
      reporting. Customize visuals with CSS userstyles, monitor progress in
      the HUD, and keep persistent game history across sessions. Cardthropic
      is tuned for desktop comfort, with clear interactions and reliable flow
      through long runs and challenging, replayable deals every day.
    </p>
  </description>
